Interface ISubscriberListener

All Known Subinterfaces:
ICompetitorsListener, IConnectionStatusListener, IControlPassingsListener, IControlRouteChangeListener, IEventMessageListener, IMapItemsListener, IPositionedItemPositionListener, IPositionListener, IPositionOffsetListener, IPositionSnappedListener, IRacesListener, IRaceStartStopTimesChangeListener, IRoutesListener, IServerTimeListener, IStartStopTimesChangeListener
public interface ISubscriberListener

All the listeners that are used for the consumer application in order to receive events from the server side have to implemented this interface.
